name: Dark Rage
Lore: 'While Qui-Gon meditated to regain strength lost during the ferocious duel, Darth Maul paced impatiently outside the energy barrier like a caged krayt dragon.',
Text: 'If opponent just initiated a duel, use 3 Force to cancel it. OR Take Deep Hatred into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If Maul has no combat cards, place an opponent''s combat card (random selection) in opponent''s Used Pile. (Immune to Sense.)',
